<info gid="2413347412" type="Plot Summary">In 2387, Earth's most successful off-world colony is under siege by a savage race of warrior-cyborgs called &quot;the Noza Empire&quot;. The Noza are seemingly invincible and the Marisian Defense Forces are severely outclassed. All hope seems lost when a trio of guns of immense power are found by the colonists and dubbed the &quot;Zillion Weapon System&quot; after the ancient civilization that created them and the substance &quot;Zillium&quot; that powers them. These guns are the only thing strong enough to destroy the Noza and are given to a team of three young colonists called &quot;the White Naughts&quot; whose members include J.J., Champ and Apple. They have been specially trained to use these weapons and are the last hope for survival for the Colonists.</info>
